data.message: The science museum is actually my favorite place in the Twin Cities. I am beyond disappointed that I will not be able to attend with you. I know this comment is useless to you, but you need to be fully aware of my crushed heart in not being able to come.

message: Hey squad, so I have this like SUPER COOL assignment to do at the Science Museum on Wednesday and I don't mind going alone but life is always much more fun with a buddy - I plan to go around 1 pm till whenever I feel done exploring and finishing the assignment (it's about dinosaurs if that's any incentive). Message me or comment if you want to come! Have a great Monday!
